///////    Install tk   /////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

No me funciona tk con rvm. Tk me funciona solo con el ruby del sistema.
En la consola, properties -> title and command -> Run command as a login shell -> if turned on rvm works and therefore tk does not work
                                                                               -> if turned off rvm does not work and tk works

sudo apt-get install libtcltk-ruby

tengo ActiveTcl? 8.6? Si lo tengo desinstalarlo (go to ActiveTcl/../../lib/rpmm/../uninstall)

descargar ActiveTcl8.5 http://www.activestate.com/activetcl/downloads

rvm reinstall ruby-2.1.1 --with-tcl --with-tk --enable-pthread

